data.description: 3-bedroom, 2 bath home in the Desert Lakes Golf Community.  NO HOA. The home has tile floors in the kitchen, both bathrooms and eating area.   Living room and bedrooms are carpeted.  Tile countertops in the kitchen and both bathrooms.  The primary bath has dule sinks with a walk-in shower.  Second bath has a tub shower. Ceiling fans in all the rooms.  The kitchen appliances are stove and microwave that is included.  Inside laundry area with entrance to the garage from the laundry room. The property is fully fenced.  This is a ideal location for golfing, river and lake access as well as close to shopping, hospitals and schools.    Buyer to verify flood plain, taxes and square footage.
